com.datastrato.gravitino.client

Class RelationalCatalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastrato.gravitino.dto.CatalogDTO
      • com.datastrato.gravitino.client.RelationalCatalog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Auditable, Catalog, SupportsSchemas, TableCatalog

    public class RelationalCatalog
extends CatalogDTO
implements TableCatalog, SupportsSchemas
    Relational catalog is a catalog implementation that supports relational database like metadata operations, for example, schemas and tables list, creation, update and deletion. A Relational catalog is under the metalake.
